OL,3,CNesbitt 'appalled' by report on
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland cardiac surgery unit
OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,FThe Health Minister has described the
OL,8,Fculture at Northern Ireland's Cardiac
OL,9,FSurgery Unit as "appalling" after UTV
OL,10,Frevealed findings of a report which
OL,11,Fsaid that the "poor behaviour" of some
OL,12,Fsenior medics had led to a
OL,13,F"significant risk to patient safety."
OL,15,FThis follows the cancellation of
OL,16,Foperations earlier this year, after
OL,17,Ffour heart surgeons refused to attend
OL,18,Ftheatre following a breakdown in
OL,19,Fworking relations between some staff
OL,20,Fmembers.
