OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,FThe report, seen by UTV last week, has
OL,8,Fraised serious concerns over the
OL,9,Fculture within the Cardiac Surgery
OL,10,FUnit and even accuses some members of
OL,11,Fstaff of being "more interested in
OL,12,Ftheir own interests than those of the
OL,13,Fpatient."
OL,15,FThe minister has now demanded that an
OL,16,Furgent meeting with the Chair of the
OL,17,FBelfast Trust in order to get answers.
