OL,7,FResponding to a question in the
OL,8,FAssembly Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,9,Fsaid: "As Minister I want to say this
OL,10,Fit was appalling to read of the staff
OL,11,Fexperiences in the Cardiac Surgery
OL,12,FUnit in the Royal Victoria Hospital.
OL,14,F"I have now been in post for 363 days
OL,15,FI have never came across anything like
OL,16,Fthis in my firsy year in post nor have
OL,17,FI recieved reports of anything similar
OL,18,Fbeing carried out previously.
