OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,F"This is incredible, as you say four
OL,8,Fconsultants working from home. I
OL,9,Factually find that hard to process in
OL,10,Fterms of delivering cardiac surgery."
OL,12,FThis follows the publishing of a
OL,13,Freport by independent inspectors who
OL,14,Fwere brought in in January to review
OL,15,Fthe Cardiac Surgery Unit.
OL,17,FThe report has not yet been made
OL,18,Fpublic but has been seen by UTV.
