OL,3,CNesbitt 'appalled' by report on
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland cardiac surgery unit
OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,FIn Belfast, almost 1000 operations are
OL,8,Fcarried out by the Trust's Cardiac
OL,9,FSurgery Unit every year.
OL,11,FThe inspection report, seen by UTV
OL,12,Flast week, highlights a "pattern of
OL,13,Fconsistently poor behaviour on the
OL,14,Fpart of a minority of senior
OL,15,Fconsultants" at the facility in the
OL,16,FRoyal Victoria hospital.
OL,18,FShockingly, in their report,
OL,19,Finspectors said: "The cultural issues
OL,20,Fin this unit represent a significant
OL,21,Frisk to patient safety."
OL,26,@tD@YOUwD@LO]{D@ROU}D@XO]
