OL,7,FThe report also said there are "areas
OL,8,Fwhere patients are placed at risk of
OL,9,Fharm, or where harm has occurred, as a
OL,10,Fresult of tensions, poor behaviours
OL,11,Fand a severe reluctance amongst staff
OL,12,Fto raise concerns."
OL,14,FMeanwhile Upper Bann MLA Dianne Dodds
OL,15,Fraised the issue in the Assembly on
OL,16,FTuesday: "The litany of issues
OL,17,Fhighlighted within it will shock
OL,18,Feveryone.
