OL,3,CNesbitt 'appalled' by report on
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland cardiac surgery unit
OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,F"It highlighted a culture of bullying
OL,8,Fand poor behaviour. An operation was
OL,9,Fcancelled because of interpersonal
OL,10,Fdifferences between personnel within
OL,11,Fthe theatre.
OL,13,F"There were also four consultants
OL,14,Fworking from home who cited "safety
OL,15,Fand wellbeing" as the reasons they
OL,16,Fcould not work within the hospital
OL,17,Fsite.
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@NO]
