OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,F"The conclusion of the report however
OL,8,Fwas the most damning stating that the
OL,9,F"cultural issues in this unit
OL,10,Frepresent a significant risk to public
OL,11,Fsafety".
OL,13,F"This was a culture that was little
OL,14,Fshort of toxic and it is one that was
OL,15,Fexacerbated by management."
