OL,3,CNesbitt 'appalled' by report on
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland cardiac surgery unit
OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,FLast week in a statement the Trust
OL,8,Fsaid: "Belfast Trust is appalled by
OL,9,Fthe staff experiences described in an
OL,10,Findependent external review into the
OL,11,Fculture and safety within the cardiac
OL,12,Fsurgical unit at the Royal Victoria
OL,13,FHospital. While we are reassured that
OL,14,Fthe cardiac surgery service remains
OL,15,Fclinically safe with excellent
OL,16,Foutcomes, we accept that there have
OL,17,Fbeen behaviours which, at times, have
OL,18,Fmade for an intolerable working
OL,19,Fenvironment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
