OL,3,CNesbitt 'appalled' by report on
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland cardiac surgery unit
OL,5,Cculture
OL,7,F"We fully acknowledge staff have felt
OL,8,Fhurt and unable to speak out. This is
OL,9,Funacceptable and we are wholeheartedly
OL,10,Fcommitted to making changes which we
OL,11,Fhave begun implementing. When patients
OL,12,Fcome into our care, they are cared for
OL,13,Fby a team of more than 200 dedicated
OL,14,Fand passionate professionals who over
OL,15,Fdeliver and whose outcomes are
OL,16,Fexcellent, as reinforced by patient
OL,17,Ffeedback, and regional and national
OL,18,Fdata.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
