OL,7,F"However we accept that behaviours
OL,8,Fmust change. We owe it to our staff
OL,9,Fand the patients they care for to get
OL,10,Fthis right. Belfast Trust has accepted
OL,11,Fthe recommendations of the independent
OL,12,Fexternal review and is working swiftly
OL,13,Fto take these forward."
